import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
const title = "Mini Tractor – Agricultural & Industrial Equipment";
const body = "<section class=\"py-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row justify-content-center\"><div class=\"col-lg-10 text-center\"><div class=\"d-inline-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2 rounded-pill border mb-3\"><img src=\"/svg/geo-alt-fill.svg\" alt=\"Service regions\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" loading=\"lazy\"> <span>USA · Switzerland · Europe · UAE &amp; GCC</span></div><h2 class=\"display-5 fw-bold mb-3\">Mini ATV Tractor for Small Farms, Gardens and Tough Terrain</h2><p class=\"lead text-secondary mb-4\">Discover a compact all-terrain tractor built for cultivation, transport and daily field work with low fuel use, strong traction and versatile attachments.</p><div class=\"d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center gap-3\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4\" href=\"/contact\">Get Your Quote This Week</a> <a class=\"btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg px-4\" href=\"#videos\">Watch Demo Videos</a> <a class=\"btn btn-success btn-lg px-4\" href=\"https://wa.me/971581262774?text=Photo%20of%20your%20businesscard%20please\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"me-2\" src=\"/svg/whatsapp.svg\" alt=\"WhatsApp\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" loading=\"lazy\">Start WhatsApp&nbsp;</a></div></div></div></div></section><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Explore the ANKEBOOT mini ATV tractor for small farms, orchards and gardens. Low fuel consumption, 700 kg load capacity, multi-tool attachments, export-ready support and real field demo videos.\"><section class=\"pb-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row g-4 align-items-stretch\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 overflow-hidden h-100\"><img class=\"img-fluid w-100\" src=\"/sites/default/files/inline-images/bereketsebze_0.jpg\" data-entity-uuid=\"0cf4c7b7-946a-4307-b047-925f73c785ae\" data-entity-type=\"file\" alt=\"ANKEBOOT mini ATV tractor working in a vegetable field\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\"></div></div><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100\"><div class=\"card-body p-4 p-xl-5\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Compact tractor solution</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">The Power of a Tractor, the Agility of an ATV</h2><p class=\"mb-3\">ANKEBOOT combines compact size, practical handling and agricultural capability in one machine. It is designed for smaller farms, orchards, vineyards, gardens and property maintenance where larger tractors are too bulky or expensive to run.</p><p class=\"mb-0\">This mini tractor helps with tilling, hauling, cultivating and transport work while remaining easy to maneuver in tight spaces and on uneven terrain.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row g-4\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 overflow-hidden h-100\"><img class=\"img-fluid w-100\" src=\"/t/9.webp\" alt=\"ANKEBOOT compact tractor on a clean white background\" width=\"1763\" height=\"674\" loading=\"lazy\"></div></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100\"><div class=\"card-body p-4\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Why buyers choose it</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">A Smarter Compact Tractor for Small-Scale Farming</h2><p>Compact tractors, also known as mini tractors or small farm tractors, are ideal for growers and landowners who need real working power without the size and fuel cost of conventional machines.</p><ul class=\"mb-0\"><li>Easy to drive and maneuver in narrow areas</li><li>Suitable for tilling, mowing, plowing and transport</li><li>Lower operating cost than many larger tractors</li><li>Built for both field work and rugged terrain</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row g-4 align-items-stretch\"><div class=\"col-lg-8\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100\"><div class=\"card-body p-4 p-xl-5\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Brand story</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">Engineered from Real Farming Experience</h2><p class=\"mb-3\">The idea behind ANKEBOOT came from people who grew up close to the land. Two farmers’ children became skilled engineers and turned their practical knowledge into a compact agricultural vehicle designed for real field conditions.</p><img class=\"img-fluid rounded-4 my-3\" src=\"/sites/default/files/inline-images/banner_1.jpg\" data-entity-uuid=\"088f7519-1a73-40a2-9cda-4c584a2755b1\" data-entity-type=\"file\" alt=\"Development banner for ANKEBOOT mini tractor project\" width=\"1866\" height=\"296\" loading=\"lazy\"><p class=\"mb-0\">After starting in 2012 and collaborating with a technical university, the team developed a highly compact 3-meter tractor platform that is now exported from Türkiye to multiple countries.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100\"><div class=\"card-body p-4\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-3\">Talk to sales</div><a class=\"btn btn-success w-100 mb-3\" href=\"https://wa.me/971581262774?text=Photo%20of%20your%20businesscard%20please\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"me-2\" src=\"/svg/whatsapp.svg\" alt=\"WhatsApp chat\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" loading=\"lazy\"></a><p><a href=\"https://wa.me/971581262774?text=Photo%20of%20your%20businesscard%20please\">Start WhatsApp&nbsp;</a></p><p class=\"mb-2\">نحن نتحدث العربية</p><ul class=\"list-unstyled small mb-4\"><li class=\"mb-2\"><img class=\"me-2\" src=\"/svg/geo-alt-fill.svg\" alt=\"Location pin\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" loading=\"lazy\">USA - Florida</li><li class=\"mb-2\"><img class=\"me-2\" src=\"/svg/geo-alt-fill.svg\" alt=\"Location pin\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" loading=\"lazy\">Switzerland</li><li class=\"mb-2\"><img class=\"me-2\" src=\"/svg/geo-alt-fill.svg\" alt=\"Location pin\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" loading=\"lazy\">Europe</li><li><img class=\"me-2\" src=\"/svg/geo-alt-fill.svg\" alt=\"Location pin\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" loading=\"lazy\">UAE &amp; GCC, Ras Al Khaimah UAE</li></ul><p><img class=\"img-fluid rounded-4\" src=\"/t/10.webp\" alt=\"Compact ATV tractor side view\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\"></p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"card-body p-4 p-xl-5 text-center\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Efficiency highlight</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">Only 2 Liters per 100 km with Strong Field Traction</h2><p class=\"lead mb-0\">A rare combination of transport efficiency, durability and working power for small farms and utility use.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row g-4\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100\"><div class=\"card-body p-4 p-xl-5\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Key advantages</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-4\">Built for the Farm. Ready for Rough Terrain.</h2><div class=\"row g-3\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div class=\"border rounded-4 p-3 h-100\"><h3 class=\"h5 mb-2\">Very Low Fuel Use</h3><p class=\"mb-0\">Consumes as little as 2 liters per 100 km, helping reduce long-term operating cost.</p></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div class=\"border rounded-4 p-3 h-100\"><h3 class=\"h5 mb-2\">Highly Durable</h3><p class=\"mb-0\">Designed for demanding daily work with durable components and practical engineering.</p></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div class=\"border rounded-4 p-3 h-100\"><h3 class=\"h5 mb-2\">Low Maintenance</h3><p class=\"mb-0\">Simple construction and accessible spare parts help lower maintenance cost.</p></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div class=\"border rounded-4 p-3 h-100\"><h3 class=\"h5 mb-2\">Strong Working Output</h3><p class=\"mb-0\">Made for field cultivation, transport tasks and attachment-based jobs in one platform.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 overflow-hidden h-100 text-center\"><img class=\"img-fluid mx-auto d-block p-3\" style=\"max-width:70%;\" src=\"/sites/default/files/inline-images/bogaybos%20Medium.png\" data-entity-uuid=\"f512fce3-ade3-4916-b19e-5c208accae65\" data-entity-type=\"file\" alt=\"ANKEBOOT compact tractor in outdoor field conditions\" width=\"640\" height=\"361\" loading=\"lazy\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row g-4 align-items-stretch\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100\"><div class=\"card-body p-4\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Cost advantage</div><h2 class=\"h3 fw-bold mb-3\">Compare Total Ownership Cost, Not Just Purchase Price</h2><p class=\"mb-0\">Fuel use, maintenance, spare parts and productivity over five years can make a major difference in the real value of your tractor investment.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 overflow-hidden h-100 text-center\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"/t/1.webp\" alt=\"ANKEBOOT ATV tractor front view\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\"><div class=\"card-body p-4\"><h2 class=\"h4 fw-bold mb-2\">One Vehicle. Endless Possibilities.</h2><p class=\"mb-0\">ATV agility plus compact tractor functionality in one multi-purpose machine.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100\"><div class=\"card-body p-4\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Reliability</div><h2 class=\"h3 fw-bold mb-3\">Compact, Tough and Ready for Daily Work</h2><p class=\"mb-2\">Original branded components</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Durable construction</p><p class=\"mb-0\">Less maintenance and longer service life</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row g-4\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100\"><div class=\"card-body p-4 p-xl-5\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Model options</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-4\">Choose the Vehicle That Fits Your Work</h2><div class=\"row g-4\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div class=\"card border rounded-4 h-100\"><div class=\"card-body\"><img class=\"img-fluid rounded-4 mb-3\" src=\"/t/7.webp\" alt=\"ANKEBOOT ATV tractor model\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\"><h3 class=\"h5 fw-bold\">ANKEBOOT ATV Tractor</h3><p class=\"mb-1\">1250 × 2500 × 1300 mm</p><p class=\"mb-1\">700 kg</p><p class=\"mb-3\">42 km/h</p><p><a class=\"btn btn-outline-primary w-100\" href=\"#specifications\">View Specifications</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div class=\"card border rounded-4 h-100\"><div class=\"card-body\"><img class=\"img-fluid rounded-4 mb-3\" src=\"/t/2.webp\" alt=\"ANKE pickup compact utility vehicle\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" loading=\"lazy\"><h3 class=\"h5 fw-bold\">ANKE Pickup</h3><p class=\"mb-1\">1250 × 3000 × 1300 mm</p><p class=\"mb-1\">600 kg</p><p class=\"mb-3\">50 km/h</p><p><a class=\"btn btn-outline-primary w-100\" href=\"#specifications\">View Specifications</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100\"><div class=\"card-body p-4 p-xl-5\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Performance proof</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">A New Standard for Small-Scale Farming</h2><ul class=\"mb-4\"><li class=\"mb-2\">Hoes more than 1000 m² of land with 1 liter</li><li>Travels 100 km with only 2 liters</li></ul><img class=\"img-fluid rounded-4\" src=\"/sites/default/files/inline-images/tarla_0.jpg\" data-entity-uuid=\"e138a118-0c59-4d2a-8696-d17eb7f84ee6\" data-entity-type=\"file\" alt=\"Mini tractor cultivating farmland during field work\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" loading=\"lazy\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\" id=\"videos\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"text-center mb-4\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Video demos</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold\">Compact Tractor Performance in Real Conditions</h2><p class=\"text-secondary mb-0\">See how the mini ATV tractor performs in cultivation, attachments and practical field work.</p></div><div class=\"row g-4\"><div class=\"col-md-4\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><p><video class=\"w-100\" controls=\"\" playsinline=\"\" preload=\"none\" poster=\"/t/compact-tractor.jpg\">\r\n                                                                                                                                    <source src=\"/mp4/compact-tractor.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\r\n                                                                                                                                  </video></p><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h5 fw-bold\">Compact Tractor Demo</h3><p class=\"mb-0 text-secondary\">Overview of handling, movement and working ability.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><p><video class=\"w-100\" controls=\"\" playsinline=\"\" preload=\"none\" poster=\"/t/mini-tractor-attachment.jpg\">\r\n                                                                                                                                    <source src=\"/mp4/mini-tractor-attachment.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\r\n                                                                                                                                  </video></p><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h5 fw-bold\">Attachment Operation</h3><p class=\"mb-0 text-secondary\">Watch the tractor working with practical farming tools.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><p><video class=\"w-100\" controls=\"\" playsinline=\"\" preload=\"none\" poster=\"/t/vidposter.jpg\">\r\n                                                                                                                                    <source src=\"/mp4/small-tractor-attachment.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\r\n                                                                                                                                  </video></p><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h5 fw-bold\">Small Tractor in the Field</h3><p class=\"mb-0 text-secondary\">See compact power and maneuverability in action.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"text-center mb-4\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Attachments</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold\">Mini Tractor Attachments for More Jobs, More Value</h2><p class=\"text-secondary mb-0\">Expand capability with field-ready tools for cultivation, transport and digging.</p></div><div class=\"row g-4\"><div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-4\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"/t/8.webp\" alt=\"Mini tractor with rotovator attachment\" width=\"918\" height=\"671\" loading=\"lazy\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h5 fw-bold\">Small Tractor with Rotovator</h3><p class=\"mb-0\">Works into very dry soil and can reach up to 25 cm depth.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-4\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"/t/5.webp\" alt=\"Mini tractor with trailer attachment\" width=\"1440\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h5 fw-bold\">Mini Tractor with Trailer</h3><p class=\"mb-0\">Pulls up to 700 kg for practical farm and transport tasks.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-4\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"/t/6.webp\" alt=\"Mini tractor with trenching bucket attachment\" width=\"2388\" height=\"1294\" loading=\"lazy\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h5 fw-bold\">Mini Tractor Trenching Bucket</h3><p class=\"mb-0\">Backhoe extension for digging and small excavation tasks.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row g-4 align-items-stretch\"><div class=\"col-lg-5\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100\"><div class=\"card-body p-4\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Buyer benefits</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">Why Mini Tractors Are a Smart Investment</h2><ul class=\"mb-0\"><li>Fuel efficiency and lower operating cost</li><li>Easy storage and transport due to compact size</li><li>Ideal for gardens, orchards and vineyards</li><li>Attachment compatibility for multiple jobs</li><li>Reliable performance with low maintenance</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><div class=\"row g-4\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"ratio ratio-16x9\"><video class=\"w-100\" controls=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"/t/vidposter.jpg\">\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                  <source src=\"/mp4/tarlasurme.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                </video></div><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h5 fw-bold\">Video 1</h3><p class=\"mb-0 text-secondary\">Rotovator on soft soil field.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"ratio ratio-16x9\"><video class=\"w-100\" controls=\"\" playsinline=\"\">\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                  <source src=\"/mp4/bronzkisa.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                </video></div><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h5 fw-bold\">Video 2</h3><p class=\"mb-0 text-secondary\">Rotovator on totally dry soil.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-12\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"ratio ratio-16x9\"><video class=\"w-100\" autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"/t/bogaybos.png\">\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                  <source src=\"/mp4/tanitimtu.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\r\n                                                                                                                                                                                </video></div><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h5 fw-bold\">Video 3</h3><p class=\"mb-0 text-secondary\">Technical university collaboration and product development.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row g-4\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"ratio ratio-16x9\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nAhct2KnlnY?rel=0\" title=\"Mini ATV tractor load and fuel demonstration\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></div><div class=\"card-body\"><h2 class=\"h4 fw-bold mb-2\">700 kg Load Capacity with 2 Liters per 100 km</h2><p class=\"mb-0 text-secondary\">Research and development that delivers practical fuel economy and useful load performance.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"ratio ratio-16x9\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/W_TgGkfsgB4?rel=0\" title=\"Durable compact tractor overview\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></div><div class=\"card-body\"><h2 class=\"h4 fw-bold mb-2\">Comfortable, Durable and Easy to Maintain</h2><p class=\"mb-0 text-secondary\">Low-cost spare parts, longer service life and everyday practicality for demanding users.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"text-center mt-4\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-lg px-5\" href=\"/contact\">Get Your Quote This Week</a></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row g-5 align-items-start\"><!-- LEFT SIDE (GUIDE - NARROWER & CLEANER) --><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 sticky-top\" style=\"top:20px;\"><div class=\"card-body p-4\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Buying Guide</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">Choose the Right Compact Tractor</h2><p class=\"text-secondary small mb-3\">Focus on what really matters for your daily work:</p><ul class=\"mb-0 small\"><li class=\"mb-2\">Required horsepower for your tasks</li><li class=\"mb-2\">Manual vs hydrostatic transmission</li><li class=\"mb-2\">Tires for field, turf or mixed use</li><li class=\"mb-2\">Needed attachments (loader, mower, etc.)</li><li>Comfort and service availability</li></ul></div></div></div><!-- RIGHT SIDE (ATTACHMENTS - BIGGER & CLEANER) --><div class=\"col-lg-8\"><div class=\"mb-4\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Attachments</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold\">Expand Your Tractor with the Right Tools</h2><p class=\"text-secondary\">Increase productivity with versatile attachments designed for real farming conditions.</p></div><!-- IMPORTANT: ONLY 2 COLUMNS --><div class=\"row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-4\"><!-- ITEM --><div class=\"col\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"/t/tool-soil-hoeing-rotovator.webp\" alt=\"Soil hoeing rotovator attachment for mini tractor\" loading=\"lazy\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h6 fw-bold\">Soil Hoeing Rotovator</h3><p class=\"small text-secondary\">120 cm working width, 6 blade rows. Ideal for efficient soil preparation.</p></div><div class=\"card-footer bg-transparent border-0 pt-0\"><a class=\"btn btn-outline-primary w-100\" href=\"/contact\">Get Price&nbsp;</a></div></div></div><!-- ITEM --><div class=\"col\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"/t/tool-spring-crowbar-cultivator.webp\" alt=\"Spring crowbar cultivator attachment\" loading=\"lazy\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h6 fw-bold\">Spring Cultivator</h3><p class=\"small text-secondary\">Breaks soil clods effectively. Custom blade configurations available.</p></div><div class=\"card-footer bg-transparent border-0 pt-0\"><a class=\"btn btn-outline-primary w-100\" href=\"/contact\">Get Price&nbsp;</a></div></div></div><!-- ITEM --><div class=\"col\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"/t/tool-plow-cultivator.webp\" alt=\"Plow cultivator attachment\" loading=\"lazy\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h6 fw-bold\">Plow Cultivator</h3><p class=\"small text-secondary\">Creates 20–30 cm deep channels for irrigation and planting.</p></div><div class=\"card-footer bg-transparent border-0 pt-0\"><a class=\"btn btn-outline-primary w-100\" href=\"/contact\">Get Price&nbsp;</a></div></div></div><!-- ITEM --><div class=\"col\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 h-100 overflow-hidden\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"/t/tool-watering-tank.webp\" alt=\"Water tank attachment for tractor\" loading=\"lazy\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h3 class=\"h6 fw-bold\">Water Tank</h3><p class=\"small text-secondary\">500–1000L options. Lightweight and ideal for field transport.</p></div><div class=\"card-footer bg-transparent border-0 pt-0\"><a class=\"btn btn-outline-primary w-100\" href=\"/contact\">Get Price&nbsp;</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4\"><div class=\"card-body p-4 p-xl-5\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Maintenance</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\">Maintenance Tips to Extend Tractor Life</h2><ul class=\"mb-0\"><li>Change oil and filters regularly</li><li>Check tire pressure and fluid levels</li><li>Store the tractor in a dry covered area</li><li>Inspect belts and hoses on schedule</li><li>Follow the manufacturer service plan</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-5\" id=\"specifications\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"text-center mb-4\"><div class=\"small text-uppercase text-primary fw-semibold mb-2\">Technical data</div><h2 class=\"fw-bold\">Mini Tractor Technical Specifications</h2><p class=\"text-secondary mb-0\">Compare the ANKEBOOT Tractor and ANKE Pickup side by side.</p></div><div class=\"card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"table table-striped align-middle mb-0\"><thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>Tractor ANKEBOOT</th><th>Pickup ANKE</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Fuel &amp; Motor Type</td><td>12 HP Diesel ANTOR brand</td><td>12 